description: This is a remix of theuniverseinmee's third installment of the Sentient Mushroom series.  Created in Daemon Lindenmayer's audio visualiser BioSphere.  The illustration of Lepiota Americana fungi glows and is set to a background of recursive moire responding to bird sounds recorded in October 2021. Contact Daemon Lindenmayer after purchase for 4k version.  https://Linktr.ee/lsystem
